1:25:25.016 --> 1:25:27.118
Then someone would havee found me,

1:25:27.118 --> 1:25:28.868
and I coulda had a normal life too.

1:25:30.700 --> 1:25:32.303
You had everything.

1:25:34.530 --> 1:25:37.330
