in the way that you thought.

1:25:41.250 --> 1:25:43.430
- You are such a liar.

1:25:43.430 --> 1:25:44.263
- Stop it.

1:25:44.263 --> 1:25:45.223
You read the journals.

1:25:46.639 --> 1:25:49.610
