I whispered something

1:25:49.610 --> 1:25:51.660
into that seashell, you read that, right?

1:25:54.150 --> 1:25:56.523
Remember what I whispered into it now?

1:25:59.230 --> 1:26:00.357
It was your name.

1:26:02.670 --> 1:26:04.663
You showed me that, do you remember?

1:26:05.690 --> 1:26:07.820
How to make a wish if you
couldn't see the stars.

1:26:07.820 --> 1:26:09.410
That's the last thing I did

1:26:09.410 --> 1:26:11.059
before I forgot about everything.

1:26:14.438 --> 1:26:16.728
You were my wish.

1:26:16.728 --> 1:26:18.380
(crying)

1:26:18.380 --> 1:26:20.130
That's why I can't have
normal relationships.

1:26:20.130 --> 1:26:21.820
That's why I couldn't deal
with Marie getting sick,

1:26:21.820 --> 1:26:24.620
because I was going to lose
her the way that I lost you.

1:26:29.380 --> 1:26:30.297
Losing you,

1:26:36.100 --> 1:26:37.343
that's what broke me.

1:26:39.969 --> 1:26:42.719
(hard breathing)

1:26:43.559 --> 1:26:46.420
Please, let Alan go.

1:26:46.420 --> 1:26:48.500
