a part of any of this.

1:26:48.500 --> 1:26:51.059
Kill me, do whatever you
want. Just let him go, please.

1:26:51.059 --> 1:26:52.210
- Why would I kill you?

1:26:56.070 --> 1:26:57.687
Now that I have you.

1:27:01.370 --> 1:27:02.593
You're my baby brother.

1:27:04.750 --> 1:27:05.873
You're home now.

1:27:07.633 --> 1:27:09.653
- Are you gonna lock me in a room?

1:27:11.092 --> 1:27:14.259
(soft dramatic music)

1:27:17.139 --> 1:27:18.430
- Do you still love me?

1:27:21.875 --> 1:27:22.992
- Yeah, I do.

1:27:22.992 --> 1:27:26.159
(soft dramatic music)

1:27:27.327 --> 1:27:28.161
- Good.

