Fuck.

1:27:47.806 --> 1:27:49.191
Fuck!

1:27:49.191 --> 1:27:52.358
(soft dramatic music)

1:27:54.343 --> 1:27:55.175
No.

1:27:57.262 --> 1:27:59.181
No no, no no, no.

1:27:59.181 --> 1:28:00.598
- It's all right.

