1:28:09.812 --> 1:28:10.853
- Come on.

1:28:10.853 --> 1:28:12.568
It's all right, it's all right.

1:28:12.568 --> 1:28:13.702
Come on.

1:28:13.702 --> 1:28:15.994
Here we go. Here we go, come on.

1:28:15.994 --> 1:28:17.411
Come on, come on.

1:28:20.742 --> 1:28:22.121
Help me up.

1:28:22.121 --> 1:28:24.263
Come on, come on, come on.

1:28:24.263 --> 1:28:25.180
Help me up.

1:28:26.896 --> 1:28:29.835
(groaning)

1:28:29.835 --> 1:28:33.003
(soft dramatic music)

1:28:35.034 --> 1:28:37.568
- [Maggie] Remember me.

1:28:37.568 --> 1:28:39.342
- It's all right, come on.

1:28:39.342 --> 1:28:40.259
Here we go.

1:28:43.611 --> 1:28:46.299
(crickets chirping)

1:28:46.299 --> 1:28:47.132
It's okay.

1:28:49.219 --> 1:28:51.636
I'm all right. I'm all right.

1:28:53.496 --> 1:28:54.330
Oh yikes.

1:28:55.657 --> 1:28:58.657
